        ("Complex AI System", "Maximizing all technical parameters produces high scores across most components, but the Consciousness Indicator Score reaches a plateau rather than increasing linearly. This suggests that if consciousness is an emergent property, it may require something beyond quantitative increases in existing properties — perhaps embodied sensory grounding, emotional valence, or biological substrate that the model does not capture. The plateau is the model\'s way of representing the hard problem: you can push every known variable to maximum and still not be certain you have produced consciousness."),
