        ("Caloric Intake Level", "The amount of food energy consumed relative to metabolic needs — excess calories increase oxidative stress, insulin signaling, and mTOR pathway activation, all of which accelerate aging, while caloric restriction is the most robust life-extending intervention across species", True),
        ("Telomere Length", "The average length of telomeric DNA across all cells — decreases with each cell division and with oxidative damage, serving as both a biomarker of biological age and a functional trigger for senescence when critically short", False),
