        "Calculate your own estimated biological age using online tools that assess sleep quality, exercise, diet, stress, and health markers — then design a personal lifestyle intervention to reduce your biological age based on your model",
        "Investigate the naked mole rat — a mammal that lives 30+ years (10x expected for its size), rarely gets cancer, and shows negligible senescence. What does this species teach us about the biology of aging and the possibility of intervention?"
